{"tid":247602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【當街斬頭】台婦遭哥哥彎刀攞命 斷頭碌地嚇壞街坊","createTime":"2017-05-18T02:42:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T04:45:27.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d825e36ee0ece3082b5a2499b95056c793a2f30f","tid":247602,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T02:42:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170518/large/1495074148_6e9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170518%2Flarge%2F1495074148_6e9c.jpg&h=75f5a279&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣高雄發生恐怖命案，苓雅區一名婦人當街遭砍頭奪命，疑兇竟是婦人哥哥。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，事發於今日早上，52歲林姓女死者陳屍在自家門口前，兇手是死者54歲哥哥。有目擊民眾指出，死者在福德路和河北路口遭一名男子用彎刀當場將頭砍下，路人嚇得驚聲尖叫，女子血濺街頭，頭顱滾到人行道的電單車道。警方獲報趕抵，封鎖現場，目前兇手躲在單位和警方對峙中。<br />\n初步調查，死者與兇手疑因金錢問題，發生糾紛，今天上午死者強行出門，死者一時氣憤持刀在家門口前殺人。"},{"pid":"ea41aeaf2828688595e6a123e5851343600cd2d6","tid":247602,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T02:45:29.000Z","msg":"今天上午死者強行出門，死者一時氣憤持刀在家門口前殺人。<br />\n自己斬自己？"},{"pid":"4a4f14d7e8a613e2819765e10c2d9fc369e09de1","tid":247602,"uid":4811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T03:01:47.000Z","msg":"真係有圓月彎刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"620bdc8a29d9e7e78b09aa2f52fdc9ee160982e4","tid":247602,"uid":59357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T03:03:02.000Z","msg":"好想睇live<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b52eddf66765a318a6bd35dc0298882e317297f8","tid":247602,"uid":62060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T03:34:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今天上午死者強行出門，死者一時氣憤持刀在家門口前殺人。<br />\n自己斬自己？</blockquote><br />\n屌你廢材報紙佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\